rows.label: qev092901_SEL0040
rows.name: Ask if she's having some trouble.

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0050
rows.name:
[ST:wide ]—Huh?
Did it look like I was having trouble?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0070
rows.name:
See, I heard that humans are unaccustomed
to interacting with aliens, so...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0080
rows.name:
Honestly, I didn't think
anyone would speak to me[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0090
rows.name: Ah, sorry if I offended you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0100
rows.name:
Say, you're a member of that organization
called BLADE too, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0110
rows.name:
If you don't mind, could you hear me out?
As you guessed, I'm in a bit of a bind[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0150
rows.name:
Say, do Qlurians really stand out so much?
Our physical features don't seem all that different...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0160
rows.name:
Well, anyway, I don't think any of us
are enjoying this attention much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092901_MSG0170
rows.name: Shall we move somewhere else to talk?[ST:wait ]
